WorkItem.Description:
Hi ,
I use Powershell, and HtmlAgilityPack processing page.
Processing supermicro product page (http://www.supermicro.com/products/chassis/3U/836/SC836TQ-R500.cfm), HTMLDocument.LoadHTML return Null.


```
add-type -Path 'e:\MyDownloads\FTP\Powershell\HtmlAgilityPack.dll'

	$HTMLDocument = New-Object HtmlAgilityPack.HtmlDocument
	$wc = New-Object System.Net.WebClient
	$wc.Encoding= [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8 

	$uri= "http://www.supermicro.com/products/chassis/3U/836/SC836TQ-R500.cfm"

	Write-Host "获取内容 " $uri ...
	$pagecontent=$wc.DownloadString($uri)

	$result = $HTMLDocument.LoadHTML($pagecontent)
	
```
